arcade.agent.helper

Class MakeTissueHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.helper.TissueHelper
      • arcade.agent.helper.MakeTissueHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Helper, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class MakeTissueHelper
extends TissueHelper
    Extension of TissueHelper for cell division.

    MakeTissueHelper is repeatedly stepped from its creation until either the cell is no longer able to proliferate or it has successfully doubled in size and is able to create a new cell object.

    Since:
    2.2
    Version:
    2.3.7
